<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFFenical1983">Fenical, William (September 1983), <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=g6RfkqCUQyQC&amp;pg=PA147&amp;dq=oxygen+percent+algae+plants&amp;sig=4tJv81njIlr7qsWD95pHcuRlffc#PPA147,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=g6RfkqCUQyQC&amp;pg=PA147&amp;dq=oxygen+percent+algae+plants&amp;sig=4tJv81njIlr7qsWD95pHcuRlffc#PPA147,M1" rel="nofollow">"Marine Plants: A Unique and Unexplored Resource"</a>, <i>Plants: the potentials for extracting protein, medicines, and other useful chemicals (workshop proceedings)</i>, DIANE Publishing, p.&#160;147, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1428923977" class="internal">ISBN 1428923977</a><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=g6RfkqCUQyQC&amp;pg=PA147&amp;dq=oxygen+percent+algae+plants&amp;sig=4tJv81njIlr7qsWD95pHcuRlffc#PPA147,M1" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=g6RfkqCUQyQC&amp;pg=PA147&amp;dq=oxygen+percent+algae+plants&amp;sig=4tJv81njIlr7qsWD95pHcuRlffc#PPA147,M1" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=g6RfkqCUQyQC&amp;pg=PA147&amp;dq=oxygen+percent+algae+plants&amp;sig=4tJv81njIlr7qsWD95pHcuRlffc#PPA147,M1</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Marine+Plants%3A+A+Unique+and+Unexplored+Resource&amp;rft.atitle=Plants%3A+the+potentials+for+extracting+protein%2C+medicines%2C+and+other+useful+chemicals+%28workshop+proceedings%29&amp;rft.aulast=Fenical&amp;rft.aufirst=William&amp;rft.au=Fenical%2C+William&amp;rft.date=September+1983&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B147&amp;rft.pub=DIANE+Publishing&amp;rft.isbn=1428923977&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dg6RfkqCUQyQC%26pg%3DPA147%26dq%3Doxygen%2Bpercent%2Balgae%2Bplants%26sig%3D4tJv81njIlr7qsWD95pHcuRlffc%23PPA147%2CM1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Deforestation"><span style="display: non